dct_description_sm: Sheet 1: Map shows plan for bridges in Robinsons Branch, as well as water depths and coordinates of specific points.
Sheet 2: Map shows plans for Monroe Street Bridge, Pennsylvania Railroad, and Elizabeth Avenue Bridge.
Sheet 3: Map shows plans for Monroe Street Bridge and others, as well as water depths.
Sheet 4: Map shows plans for various bridges in Union County, and also includes water depths.
